{"tid":1923543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克無視京施壓與台交往","createTime":"2020-03-13T06:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T09:14:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"86545b620acead6047744a843632217ef68994e9","tid":1923543,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200313/2YI32Y5ZQHBVHDETLUDG5ANXCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200313%2F2YI32Y5ZQHBVHDETLUDG5ANXCM%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=a386ecab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200313%2F2YI32Y5ZQHBVHDETLUDG5ANXCM%2F&h=be5d2a70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200313/2YI32Y5ZQHBVHDETLUDG5ANXCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n捷克無視京施壓與台交往<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200313/large/1584029326_a0ef.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200313%2Flarge%2F1584029326_a0ef.gif&h=e09ba875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捷克總統澤曼（左）昨在總統府與總理、外交部長等高層進行例行性會議。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐捷克大使館早前因為捷克參議院議長計劃訪台，致函捷克總統府警告將向在華捷克企業作出報復。捷克政府周三（11日）召開例行高層會議後強調，捷克獨立決定外交政策，拒絕北京任何形式的施壓，並稱有意在不違反「一個中國」原則下與台灣發展文化經貿關係。<br />\n<br />\n總統︰有獨立主權<br />\n<br />\n捷克參議院前議長柯佳洛原計劃上月訪台，但在今年1月底因病猝逝。中國駐布拉格大使張建敏在1月曾致函捷克總統府，指若捷克的資深議員按計劃訪台，包括大眾汽車子公司斯柯達、捷信集團等在華營運捷克企業「將受到影響」。捷克總理巴比什稱張建敏的行為無法接受，將要求中方撤換大使。<br />\n<br />\n捷克總統與政府最高層前日舉行例會後發表聲明，強調捷克政府有獨立主權，「不受外部影響且以國家利益為重心來決定外交政策，在不違反捷克和歐盟長期維持的一個中國政策下，維持與台灣的經濟和文化合作關係。」聲明亦稱，捷中雙邊經貿存在嚴重不平衡，因為捷克對華出口額僅為進口額的十分之一。新任參議院議長維特齊表示，有意提案要求中方撤換大使，但並無回應是否將會訪台。根據捷克憲法，參議院議長是僅次於總統的政府第二號人物。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部歐洲司副司長陳詠韶昨表示，維特齊上任不久，尚在規劃行程，外交部將持續關注捷克政壇高層近期針對出訪行程的討論。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"f4ad4289b05371dedcec8a09c5ecb3c161740d9f","tid":1923543,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0856c15875ca1ba639d961e7424efea62b330d9f","tid":1923543,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"捷克有無D乜嘢軍備係勁？<br />\n<br />\n假如獨立成功, 將來一定要同佢買貨！"},{"pid":"d18de513c24e71874f235a2cb27c0507f47270d7","tid":1923543,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"又干預別國事務"},{"pid":"923606d9dfa4293ebfb74c9cf7662511f2385aed","tid":1923543,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"包括大眾汽車子公司斯柯達、捷信集團等在華營運捷克企業「將受到影響」。捷克總理巴比什稱張建敏的行為無法<br />\n<br />\n呢啲真係惡棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1674e65fa32bf856fdd7e52dad46bc34ff66132a","tid":1923543,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"捷克好啵 Taiwan no.1"},{"pid":"34a62ad4b14abc9c257739bb28ca1b5ab523c739","tid":1923543,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3487cab7e459bdc1b770e006237466b7dede756","tid":1923543,"uid":340004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0856c15875ca1ba639d961e7424efea62b330d9f","tid":1923543,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"捷克有無D乜嘢軍備係勁？<br />\n<br />\n假如獨立成功, 將來一定要同佢買貨！"},"c